Package org.parosproxy.paros.extension

Class ExtensionHookView

java.lang.Object
org.parosproxy.paros.extension.ExtensionHookView
public class ExtensionHookView extends Object
The object to add/hook components to the main UI components.

The components added through the hook are removed when the extension is unloaded.

Note: This class is not thread-safe, the components should be added only through the thread that hooks the extension.

Since:
1.0.0
